An HTTP file server that serves static files from a configurable directory on the hosting computer.

- Nice Ascii art on terminal
- Nice to have: Also support directories, turn it into an interactive html you can click around on

- Extend the code. Keep it simple. try to immitate golang. Use as few object oriented features as possible.
- Run the code with: `make run`
- Test it with: `curl -i 0.0.0.0:8888`
